Digital Marketing Executive
Confidential Company - ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/04 07:54:25
Ref. JB3046961
Job Description
•	Responsible for building business and developing strategies for obtaining more sales for the company
•	Connect with customers via online channels to build the business
•	Works cohesively with all stake holders – external and internal to ensure business gains growth
•	Create an annual operating plan for the business
•	Develop strong marketing campaigns for brands to ensure sustainable improvement
•	Has good amount of knowledge in SEO and digital and online marketing
•	Has basic knowledge about programming or web designing (HTML)
•	Computer literate
•	IT Background is an advantage
•	Should presently be available for interview in the UAE
•	Good communication skills
